{"tid":658804,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩灰得過搭地鐵","createTime":"2018-05-09T09:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T09:40:56.000Z","uid":5348,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"66cd5e47e0301d4b34a16625dc7a8000d12e6e07","tid":658804,"uid":5348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:36:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我岩岩放工搭西鐵翻屋企<br />\n跟住我見到有兩個空位 一個呀嬸坐緊 而另一個位比學妹妹坐緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n周圍未發現廢老既出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我緊係啦啦林坐埋去學生妹身邊 感受佢既餘香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜佢只係坐左一個站就落車<br />\n惡夢黎啦 佢落左車 但上左兩個印度腸出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩個仲要夾撚住我黎坐 好似想感受我既餘香咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個頭向左又落係 向右又唔係 佢地身上陣咖哩味好撚攻鼻呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c2d32cf5859fc6279c1a09af79ac735f104d45","tid":658804,"uid":16067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:36:43.000Z","msg":"爽完唔洗還啊?"},{"pid":"82b4ae2e941355e3e1fac6deafbb23941ee4236b","tid":658804,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:36:55.000Z","msg":"下個站落車係第2個車廂上返"},{"pid":"723a5940efa97a98ffc5118c70cd5e871ce80d0b","tid":658804,"uid":101063,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"82b4ae2e941355e3e1fac6deafbb23941ee4236b","tid":658804,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:36:55.000Z","msg":"下個站落車係第2個車廂上返"},"cit